frameDefinitions: An Agent acts so as to cause some process to begin again after an interruption or suspension.

An Item is located at the top end of a scale of importance or social rank (or some other Attribute) in comparison to other members of a Contrast_set (usually, implicit) that is otherwise similar in kind to the Item.
An entity goes through several versions, from initial to final.
An Entity is presented as having been seen or experienced by a (typically generic and backgrounded)
A Figure is (stably) located with respect to a Ground in terms of how the distance between them compares to some general or contextually relevant scale.
An Entity has existed for a length of time, the Age.
frameExamples: The two countries <t>revived</t> diplomatic relations after a lull of five years.
The <t>main</t> problem is that the administration has not yet clarified 'Regime change.' INI
Susanna Fulton's work is <t>new</t> to me.
This building is twenty thousand years <t>old</t>.
listRoleDefinitions: A sentient being acts with the intention of causing a process to begin again.
The process which begins again after a suspension.
The period of time during which the process is suspended.
An animate or inanimate entity, a force, or event that causes the process to resume. Volitionality is not a necessary characteristic of Causes.
The time at which the process is restarted.
The location where the <fen>Agent</fen> causes the <fen>Process</fen> to resume.
An <fen>Item</fen> is the foremost thing in the <fen>Contrast_set</fen>.
This role identifies the domain (usually temporally or spatially defined) within which the <fen>Item</fen> is primary among its kind.
The <fen>Contrast_set</fen> is a group of entities similar to the <fen>Item</fen> out of which the <fen>Item</fen> is the most preeminent.
The <fen>Item</fen> is one version among several versions (which may or may not yet exist), progressively getting closer to a final version.
A concrete thing or abstract phenomenon or fact that is assessed in terms of how well recognizable it is to a <fen>Cognizer</fen>.
The (typically non-specific and backgrounded) sentient being for whom the <fen>Entity</fen> possesses a specified level of recognizability.
The deviation of the actual level of recognizability of the <fen>Entity</fen> from the level specified by the target.
The <fen>Ground</fen> serves as a basis for describing the location of the <fen>Figure</fen>.
The <fen>Figure</fen> is perceived as located relative to a certain <fen>Ground</fen> location. The figure can be an entity or an event.
The <fen>Figures</fen> are items which mutually serve to identify the location of the other items.
The period of time during which the locative relation between <fen>Figure</fen> and <fen>Ground</fen> obtains.
The <fen>Entity</fen> for which a particular age is under consideration.
The feature of an <fen>Entity</fen> which is a function of the amount of time that the <fen>Entity</fen> has existed.
A quantity or other characterization of the <fen>Entity</fen>'s age.
A modifier expressing  the deviation of the <fen>Age</fen> from the norm.
The Frame Element <fen>Expressor</fen> marks expressions that indicate a body part, gesture or other expression of the <fen>Entity</fen> that reflect its age.
The <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Entity</fen> is at a particular <fen>Age</fen>.
listRoleExamples: <fex>The driver</fex> restarted the truck after it stalled.
The two countries revived diplomatic relations <fex>after a lull of five years</fex>.
<fex>The spring rains</fex> restarted the flow of the stream.
This state reinstated the death penalty <fex>in 1975</fex>.
The two nations revived relations <fex>in Geneva</fex> during the latest round of talks.
The foremost band <fex>in the world of the 1960's</fex> was clearly the Beatles.
Our discussion has raised a number of issues, foremost <fex>among them</fex> time.
He gave <fex>an address</fex> quite familiar to the chauffeur.
The information used to illustrate the concept is familiar <fex>to the reader</fex>.
He gave an address <fex>quite</fex> familiar to the chauffeur.
<fex>The two waffle houses</fex> are so close together they can throw ingredients across the road to each other .
'Who's there?' she barked. 'Ensign Kim, ma'me,' the youngish voice of Voyager's young Harry Kim came over the comm line. '
